## Legend titles

The `name` arguments modifies the title for legends created automatically for each mapping  

:::{.med-code}

::: {.cell hash='visualization_cache/revealjs/unnamed-chunk-10_14d601fedfcc02635ec3d5954fc38d8c'}

```{.r .cell-code}
aes(x,y, color = var1, shape = var2)+
	scale_color_manual(values=c('red','blue'), 
	                   name= 'Variable One')+
  scale_shape_manual(values=c(20,21),
	                   name = 'Variable Two')
```
:::


